                            <comment id="17388018" author="klcopp" created="Tue, 27 Jul 2021 12:33:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is incomplete because if the table is dropped, all related compactions are cleared from metadata. So here we&apos;re trying to fail a compaction that doesn&apos;t exist.&lt;/p&gt;

